snippet.title: You’re Not Behind (Yet): What I Would Learn Before the 2026 AI Shift
snippet.description:
In this video, I cover 10 of my own predictions for AI in the year 2026.  
This video will prepare you and teach you how to position yourself for success in 2026 with the constant change of AI and vibe coding technology.

So much to look forward to.

Let me know in the comments below what you think of these predictions and if you have any other AI or vibe coding predictions for 2026! 

Also- if you enjoyed this video, the best way to support the continuation of more videos is by liking, sharing and subscribing to my channel.  Appreciate the support and I'll see you for the next one!

If you've always had an app idea but were limited by time, money, technical skills, I highly recommend trying out Vibecode App.  Me and my cofounders have been working hard on this tool for most of 2025 and we want to enable 1M people to build software without writing a single line of code.

Try building your first mobile app completely for free here: https://vibecode.go.link/1ozxZ
 ➡️using promo code "2026"


My Socials:
https://x.com/rileybrown
https://www.linkedin.com/in/riley-brown-7441b1101/
https://www.instagram.com/realrileybrown/

02:35 Google's Integration with Everyday Tools
07:15 Apple's Mini App Revolution
09:22 The YouTube Moment for Software
13:33 The Craving for Connection
17:15 Anthropic's Edge in the Coding War
19:58 The Future of AI Agents and Automations
22:18 My Boldest Predictions
22:30 Zuckerberg Will Bring AI Video to Instagram
22:51 Elon Musk's Video Game Builder on X
23:08 Zero AI Social Media Platforms
23:21 Divine Vine Platform
24:30 Final Thoughts on AI Trends for 2026
